'''嗜酸乳桿菌'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Lactobacillus acidophilus''}}）又稱'''A菌'''，是[[乳桿菌屬|乳桿菌屬]]的一種。A菌適合生存在酸性、30°C（86°F）的環境中，存在人類、動物的[[腸胃道|腸胃道]]和[[口腔|口腔]]<ref>{{cite web  | title = Bacteria Genomes – LACTOBACILLUS ACIDOPHILUS  | publisher = [[European_Bioinformatics_Institute|European Bioinformatics Institute]]  | url = http://www.ebi.ac.uk/2can/genomes/bacteria/Lactobacillus_acidophilus.html  | accessdate = 2007-08-22  | archive-date = 2013-06-26  | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6Hfe5gIZi?url=http://www.ebi.ac.uk/2can  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>，和大部分的[[乳酸菌|乳酸菌]]一樣能夠將[[乳糖|乳糖]]轉變為[[乳酸|乳酸]]。其相關的菌種還能產生[[乙醇|乙醇]]、[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]、[[乙酸|乙酸]]。A菌無法在溫度與濕度過高、陽光直射的環境生存。能在相對較低pH值（pH 5.0以下）穩定生長，最佳生長溫度約為37°C<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0168160500003615|pages=241–247|title=Study of the cryotolerance of Lactobacillus acidophilus: effect of culture and freezing conditions on the viability and cellular protein levels|journal=International Journal of Food Microbiology|volume=59|issue=3|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1016/s0168-1605(00)00361-5|author=Leı̈la Bâati, Cathy Fabre-Gea, Daniel Auriol, Philippe J Blanc|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629013746/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0168160500003615|dead-url=no}}</ref>。部分的嗜酸乳桿菌菌種帶有[[益生菌|益生菌]]的特質<ref name="Ljungh_2006">{{cite journal |author=Ljungh A, Wadström T |title=Lactic acid bacteria as probiotics |journal=Curr Issues Intest Microbiol |volume=7 |issue=2 |pages=73–89 |year=2006 |pmid=16875422}}</ref>。這些菌種在商業上因此用於多種奶製品中，有時還會跟[[嗜熱鏈球菌|嗜熱鏈球菌]]（{{lang|la|''Streptococcus thermophilus''}}）和[[保加利亚乳杆菌|保加利亞亞種德氏乳桿菌]]（{{lang|la|''Lactobacillus delbrueckii ''subsp.'' bulgaricus''}}）配搭用於製作嗜酸型的酸奶飲品。

